[h1]GK Ascension Pacing[/h1]

Dynamically scales ascension situation speed based on game year. Early rushers face slower progress, while late adopters ascend faster — closing the gap without hard time gates.

[h2]Features[/h2]

[h3]Ascension Speed Scaling[/h3]
[list]
[*] Ascension situations run at 0.5x speed at game start, reaching vanilla speed around year 2250
[*] Late-game ascension (2300+) runs at up to 2.5x speed
[*] Smooth quadratic curve — no hard cutoffs
[/list]

[h3]Patience Bonus[/h3]
[list]
[*] Empires without an ascension path gain scaling bonuses from year 2240: pop workforce and founder species growth — growing each year with diminishing returns
[*] On ascending, the bonus is halved and locked in permanently
[*] Chosen / Corporate Chosen civics do not count as ascended, since they still require the Mind Over Matter AP
[/list]

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]
Overwrites 8 vanilla ascension situations. Not compatible with other mods that modify the same situation definitions.

